<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.156541>
    dc:description "FIGURES 17 – 20, Caragonia monstruosa (Signoret) comb. nov., female genitalia. (17) Sternite VII, first valvifer, tergite VIII, pygofer, gonoplac, and anal tube, lateral view (internal sternite VIII not illustrated); (18) sternite VII, tergite VIII, and internal sternite VIII, dorsal view; (19) sternite VII, pygofer, ovipositor valvulae (bases not illustrated), and gonoplacs, ventral view; (20) base of first valvula and first valvifer, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/156541/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

